race.comment: MARETH (5) Harry Angel filly resuming from a lengthy break. Showed ability in three runs in Victoria and proven in all conditions. Looks primed for this after the two slick trials and maps to get the right run. KITESURFING (4) back from an eight-month break. Chipped away late on debut when a tidy third over 1000m at Hawkesbury on April 5. Wasn't asked to do much in her latest trial and drawn to get the gun run. ARTGIRL (1) returned for her second campaign with a fast finishing third over 1100m at this track. Stays at the trip and comes here with race fitness on her side. BOTTLES OF SHELLS (2) Wootton Bassett filly out of Group winning mare Champagne Cuddles on debut for the Waterhouse & Bott yard. Had a total of five trials leading into this and sure to be well educated. Keep safe.
